data.description: "Welcome to your spacious three-bedroom haven in the sought-after Goose Lake Township, Morris! Situated on a sprawling 1.09-acre lot adorned with mature trees, this property offers a serene escape.   Pulling into the ample driveway you will see the large two-car, heated garage which is perfect for both vehicles and storage. As you step inside, you'll discover a versatile bonus room, allowing you to unleash your creativity - whether it becomes a den, family room, office, studio or a combination of these spaces. Next the open concept kitchen and dining room features a 9-foot sliding glass door providing a seamless connection to the outdoors.    Convenience meets functionality with a first-floor laundry room and full bath. The home a unique 1/2 bath located in the main floor bedroom, making it an ideal choice for a guest, or in-law suite. The primary bedroom on the second floor is generously sized, complete with a walk-in closet and skylights. The second bedroom mirrors the primary in size and enjoys its skylights. There is also a dedicated storage room on the 2nd floor to ensure your belongings are neatly organized. Updates galore! All new doors, windows a concrete patio (41 x 16) in 2021. A kitchen update complete with a black stainless steel appliances, plumbing, fresh flooring and carpet, modernized half bath, two full baths helped pass the time in 2020. The doors and trim, crafted from knotty Alder, lend character to the interior.  Enjoy some peace of mind with the new osmosis system, air tank, whole house filter, tankless/on demand water system and furnace/ac are also recent additions. In addition to all the wonderful features of this home, it comes with water rights to four different lakes in our welcoming community. Enjoy the beauty of the water and all the recreational opportunities it provides, making this property even more appealing for those who love lakeside living. **** This property is a true gem, offering modern amenities and plenty of space both inside and out. Don't miss the opportunity to call it your own. Schedule a viewing today!"
